{"tid":1592100,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(嚴正聲明) 我本人在此宣布，任何小圈子對話會的人都不能代表本人","createTime":"2019-09-24T12:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T08:48:25.000Z","uid":40663,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6e75d8fab2d8b00b4b14dfa40828311032b4ead4","tid":1592100,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:38:54.000Z","msg":"鑑於對話會越嚟越近，以下嘅垃圾post一定會越嚟越多<br />\n<br />\n「是咁的，我被抽中出席林鄭月娥個對話會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592003</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">為免呢個垃圾政權一陣話本平台已派人出席或已同政府溝通</span></strong>，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>本人在此宣佈，</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>出席對話會嘅人，冇一個可以代表我，我一早開展咗對話，我已經話咗，</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>回應就係對話，答啦仆街政府</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求人手置頂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"e6daf4fb88f88afd5a7986eda2087566c6e90340","tid":1592100,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:39:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"801caa826cd0a43e85fd5468fe4a65b920b3f4dd","tid":1592100,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33gKqBf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33gKqBf.png&h=13ef2b7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e28a879207679a73f4910c5c415d80d6725eaf0","tid":1592100,"uid":40663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0